title: IndeX (demo Reggae songs)
description:
"A modern interpretation of the real old-school dub-reggae from Jamaica"



IndeX is a Dutch Reggae-band, located the southern town of Venlo, and counts a handful of members;

Marc (bass)
Daniel (drums/vocals)
Patrick (guitar)
Saba (keyboard)
Niels (vocals/guitar)

Their name, "IndeX", already exists since the year 2000. In the early beginning, the band started as a punk-band, but nowadays they make music especially based on reggae, with many influences from other styles, such as punk, funk, ska, dub and more..

This torrent includes five songs, as heard through their web-site;

Intro  		5:57
Babylon 	4:32
Secret 		7:59
My Brother 	3:31
All One 	6:13
